                    "editor": "<p style=\"color:#475569; font-family:Outfit; font-size:16px; line-height:1.8;\">To redefine luxury through the lens of intentionality. MK GLAMZ exists to bridge the gap between high-performance artistry and the effortless grace of daily ritual. We believe beauty is not an addition, but an unveiling.</p>"
